3 for the whole week , please !	the weather next_few_days for mountain_view is going to be a series of ups and downs from drizzle on tuesday to a dry on monday and to stormy on saturday the highs are forecast to be near 100f with lows near 20f
4 thank you so much for the information	you are welcome have a good day

3 for the whole week , please !	the weather next_few_days for san_mateo is going to be a series of ups and downs from rain on wednesday to a drizzle on friday and to dew on sunday the highs are forecast to be near 100f with lows near 20f
4 thank you so much for the information	you are welcome have a good day
